<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>🏆 人生成就系统</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
            background: #0d0d1a;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .app {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 560px;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* ===== 顶部 ===== */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a3e 0%, #2d1b69 100%);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 32px 24px 28px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        .header::before {
            content: '🏆';
            position: absolute;
            right: -10px;
            top: -10px;
            font-size: 80px;
            opacity: 0.08;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .header .sub {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        /* ===== 进度总览 ===== */
        .overview {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
边界半径：16px；
            padding: 18px 20px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        .ov-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .ov-header .rank {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        }
        .ov-header .rank strong {
            color: #ffd700;
        }
        .ov-header .pct-big {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffd700;
        }
        .ov-bar {
            height: 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .ov-bar .fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffd700, #ff6b6b);
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: width 0.8s ease;
        }
        .ov-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .ov-stats span strong { font-size: 16px; }
        .ov-stats .done-s strong { color: #4caf50; }
        .ov-stats .todo-s strong { color: #ff9800; }

        /* ===== 筛选 ===== */
        .filter-bar {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .filter-btn {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            background: transparent;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .filter-btn.active {
            background: rgba(255,215,0,0.12);
            border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
            color: #ffd700;
        }
        .filter-btn:hover {
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        }

        .section-label {
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 8px 0 14px;
        }

        /* ===== 成就卡片 ===== */
        .achieve-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .achieve-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 20px 20px 18px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .achieve-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        /* 左侧金色装饰条 - 完成时显示 */
        .achieve-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 4px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
            transition: 0.4s;
        }
        .achieve-card.done::before {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffd700, #ff9800);
            width: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
        }

        /* 已完成样式 */
        .achieve-card.done {
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.06);
            border-color: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.15);
        }

        /* ===== 成就内容布局 ===== */
        .card-top {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        /* 奖杯图标 - 大号 */
        .trophy-icon {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .achieve-card.done .trophy-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ff9800);
            border-color: #ffd700;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(255,215,0,0.25);
        }

        .card-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        /* 成就名称 */
        .achieve-name {
            font-size: 19px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .achieve-card.done .achieve-name {
            color: #ffd700;
        }

        /* 达成条件 */
        .achieve-condition {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            margin-top: 6px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding-right: 10px;
        }
        .achieve-card.done .achieve-condition {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
        }

        /* ===== 底部信息 ===== */
        .card-bottom {
            display: flex;
justify-Content：间距；
对齐项：居中；
margin-top:14px；
垫顶：12px；
上边框：1px实体rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        }

/* 完成率数据 */
.完工率{
显示：柔性；
对齐项：居中；
间隙：8px；
font-size:13px；
        }
.rate-bar-wrap{
宽度：80px；
高度：4px；
背景：rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
边界半径：4px；
溢出：隐藏；
        }
.rate-bar-wrap.rate-fill{
高度：100%；
边界半径：4px；
背景：线性梯度(90度，#4caf50，#8bc34a)；
过渡：宽度0.6s缓动；
        }
.rate-text{
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
font-weight:500；
空白：noWrap；
        }
.rate-text.pct-num{
color：#4caf50；
font-weight:700；
        }

/* 状态标签 + 操作 */
        .card-actions {
显示：柔性；
对齐项：居中；
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .status-tag {
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
font-weight:600；
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .status-tag.todo {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        .status-tag.done {
            background: rgba(76,175,80,0.12);
color：#4caf50；
            border: 1px solid rgba(76,175,80,0.2);
        }

        .mark-btn {
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: none;
font-size:13px；
font-weight:600；
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        .mark-btn.complete {
            background: rgba(255,215,0,0.12);
            color: #ffd700;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
        }
        .mark-btn.complete:hover {
            background: rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
        }
        .mark-btn.undo {
背景：rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        }
        .mark-btn.undo:hover {
            background: rgba(255,82,82,0.1);
            color: #ff5252;
            border-color: rgba(255,82,82,0.2);
        }

        .delete-btn {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
字体大小：16px；
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 4px 6px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .delete-btn:hover {
            color: #ff5252;
            background: rgba(255,82,82,0.1);
        }

        /* ===== 添加区域 ===== */
        .add-section {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        .add-section .add-label {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
font-size:13px；
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .add-name-row {
显示：柔性；
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .add-name-row input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            outline: none;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
颜色：白色；
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        .add-name-row input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        .add-name-row input:focus {
            border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.4);
背景：rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }

        .add-desc-row {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .add-desc-row input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            outline: none;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        .add-desc-row input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        .add-desc-row input:focus {
            border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.4);
背景：rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }

        .add-rate-row {
显示：柔性；
            gap: 10px;
对齐项：居中；
        }
        .add-rate-row input {
宽度：80px；
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            outline: none;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
颜色：白色；
文本对齐：居中；
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        .add-rate-row input:focus {
            border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.4);
        }
        .add-rate-row input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        .add-rate-row span {
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .add-rate-row button {
            margin-left: auto;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ff9800);
            color: #1a1a2e;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
font-weight:700；
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .add-rate-row button:active { transform: scale(0.95); }

        /* ===== 预设成就 ===== */
        .preset-section {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .preset-section .p-label {
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .preset-grid {
显示：柔性；
            flex-wrap: wrap;
间隙：8px；
        }
        .preset-item {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
font-size:13px；
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .preset-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255,215,0,0.08);
            border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
            color: #ffd700;
        }
        .preset-item .p-name { font-weight: 600; }
        .preset-item .p-rate {
            font-size: 11px;
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
margin-top:2px；
        }

/* ===== 空状态 ===== */
.空白状态{
文本对齐：居中；
填料：60px20px；
颜色：rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }
.空白状态。图标{font-size:64px；bargin-bottom:12px；}
.空白状态p{font-size:16px；}

/* ===== 响应式 ===== */
@media(最大宽度：480px){
正文{padding:12px；}
.header{padding:24px18px20px；}
.header h1{font-size:24px；}
.trophy-icon{宽度：44px；高度：44px；字体大小：22px；}
.acheve-name{font-size:17px；}
.ceeve-condition{font-size:13px；}
.card-bottom{flex-direction:column；align-items:flex-start；gap:10px；}
.card-actions{宽度：100%；对齐内容：flex-end；}
.add-name-row{flex-direction:column；}
.add-rate-row{flex-wrap:wrap；}
        }

/* ===== 完成弹窗 ===== */
.Toast{
位置：固定；
top:20px；
左侧：50%；
transform:translateX(-50%)translateY(-100px)；
背景：rgba(76，175，80，0.95)；
背景滤镜：模糊(12px)；
颜色：白色；
填料：16px28px；
边界半径：16px；
字体大小：16px；
font-weight:600；
盒影：08px40pxrgba(76，175，80，0.3)；
过渡：变换0.5s三次贝塞尔(0.34，1.56，0.64，1)；
Z指数：999；
指针事件：无；
        }
.toast.show{
transform:translateX(-50%)translateY(0)；
        }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app">
<! -- ===== 顶部 ===== -->
<div class="header">
<h1>🏆 人生成就系统</h1>
<div class="sub">解锁你的人生里程碑</div>

<div class="overview">
<div class="over-header">
<div class="rank">🏅 成就等级<strong id="rank Display">青铜</strong></div>
<div class="pct-big"id="overallPct">0%</div>
</div>
<div class="over-bar">
<div class="fill"id="overallBar"style="width:0%；"></div>
</div>
<div class="ov-stats">
<span class="done-s">🏆 已解锁<strong id="doneTotal">0</strong></span>
<span class="todo-s">🔒 未解锁<strong id="todoTotal">0</strong></span>
<span>📊 总计<strong id="grandTotal">0</strong></span>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<! -- ===== 添加自定义成就 ===== -->
<div class="add-section">
<div class="add-label">✏️ 自定义成就</div>
<div class="add-name-row">
<输入类型="文本"id="输入名称"占位符="成就名称，如：学有所成！"maxlength="30"/>
</div>
<div class="add-desc-row">
<input type="text"id="inputDesc"占位符="达成条件，如：成功通过高等教育，拿到大学毕业证书"maxlength="100"/>
</div>
<div class="add-rate-row">
<输入类型="数字"id="输入速率"占位符="38"最小="0"最大="100"/>
<span>%的人已完成</span>
<button id="addCustomBtn">➕添加成就</button>
</div>
</div>

<! -- ===== 预设推荐 ===== -->
<div class="预设节">
<div class="p-label">📌 推荐成就(点击一键添加)</div>
<div class="预设网格"id="预设网格"></div>
</div>

<! -- ===== 筛选 ===== -->
<div class="filter-bar">
<button class="filter-btn active"data-filter="all">全部</button>
<按钮class="filter-btn"data-filter="done">✅ 已解锁</button>
<按钮class="filter-btn"data-filter="todo">🔒 未解锁</button>
</div>

<div class="section-label"id="listLabel">--成就列表--</div>

<! -- ===== 成就列表 ===== -->
<div class="实现列表"id="实现列表"></div>

<! -- ===== 空状态 ===== -->
<div class="empty-state"id="emptyState">
<div class="icon">🎯</div>
<p>还没有成就记录</p>
</div>

<! -- ===== 提示弹窗 ===== -->
<div class="toast"id="toast"></div>
</div>

